<%= render "layouts/flash" %>

<div class="justify-content-center alert alert-info">
    <i class="sidenav-icon fa fa-info-circle"></i>
    Through this simple verifier you can check if a specific file has been generated by a certain
    entity registered in Eschooltul and its hash has been stamped in Blockchain (Sawtooth). 
    If the result is positive, it means that the file has not been altered and that its hash was generated
    and stamped on the indicated date, i.e. the content of the corporate document is authentic.
    If you have any doubts about the legal validity of the document, please contact us.
</div>

<%= simple_form_for :validator, url: validators_path do |f| %>
  <%= f.input :file, as: :file%>
  <%= f.button :submit, "Validate report"%>
<% end %>